        {
            "text": "<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial\">为确保 WishPost 官网 (</span><a href=\"https://wishpost.cn/\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none;\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(17, 85, 204); font-family:arial\">https://wishpost.cn</span></a><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial\">) 在即将来临的旺季保持最佳的运营状态，自 UTC 时间2020年11月10日凌晨0时起，UTC 时间2019年1月1日凌晨0时之前创建的运单的信息将被迁移至历史数据查询网站 (</span><a href=\"https://archive.wishpost.cn/\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none;\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(17, 85, 204); font-family:arial\">https://archive.wishpost.cn</span></a><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial\">)。届时，商户将只能在该网站查询这些运单的信息，在官网 (</span><a href=\"https://wishpost.cn/\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none;\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(17, 85, 204); font-family:arial\">https://wishpost.cn</span></a><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial\">) 上将查询不到。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:16px\">商户可以使用登录</span><a href=\"https://wishpost.cn/\" style=\"font-size: 16px; text-decoration-line: none;\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial\"> </span><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(17, 85, 204); font-family:arial\">https://wishpost.cn</span></a><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:16px\"> 所用的账号和密码登录</span><a href=\"https://archive.wishpost.cn/\" style=\"font-size: 16px; text-decoration-line: none;\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial\"> </span><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(17, 85, 204); font-family:arial\">https://archive.wishpost.cn</span></a><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:16px\">。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:16px\">请注意，</span><a href=\"https://archive.wishpost.cn/\" style=\"font-size: 16px; text-decoration-line: none;\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(17, 85, 204); font-family:arial\">https://archive.wishpost.cn</span></a><span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:16px\"> 仅可用于查看历史运单信息和物流跟踪信息，无法进行注册、创建新运单或更新现有运单等操作。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"background-color:transparent; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial; font-size:16px\">如您对此有任何疑问，请联系您的客户经理。感谢您的配合！</span></p>\n",
